    - Deborah L. Smouse]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Recently, I had the delightful privilege of going on a tour with Horse Farm Tours. Our tour guide was David, who provided an excellent tour experience. David took us to Keeneland, where we toured the grounds. We drove past beautiful Calumet Farm and then travelled on to one of the breeding farms where we were able to tour the barns and learn from the workers. We learned all about the history of horse breeding there. It was a beautiful day and with our wonderful, knowledgable tour guide David, it was a great experience. I would definitely recommend!</p><h3>- Deborah L. Smouse</h3>]]></content:encoded></item></channel></rss>